[11]The plant of King Long covering a total area of 200,000 square meters, with over 1800 employees, of which 400 are technical engineers, 30 are graduates specialized, that play a key role in different sections such as production management, quality control, finance, sales and after-sales service .
[12]Thanks to a policy of production and report quality, aggressive price, the King Long has first taken a leading position among the manufacturers of the national bus market in the coach chinese which is revealed to be the largest in the world.The King Long has cared to take a close collaboration with a large number of parts suppliers with international reputation, including German companies MAN and ZF, american companies Cummins, Dana and Neway, French company Telma, and japanese Nissan, and Hino and the Italian company IVECO.The King Long currently offers a range of 5 main products, which are in their turn divided into more than 50 categories, covering virtually all categories of buses and coaches between 6 and 13 metres, gaining popularity in the bus industry, tourism, and in the market for city buses.The products of King Long are sold currently on many foreign markets, including India, Costa Rica, Bulgaria, Singapore, Italy, Saudi Arabia, Iraq, Cyprus, Lebanon, Malta, the United States, Argentina, Barbados, Hong Kong, Hungary, Macau, and Thailand.
